title: IndeTrendence Day 5/8: Tekashi 6IX9ine, CostCo, NBA, Al Gore
itunes:title: IndeTrendence Day 5/8: Tekashi 6IX9ine, CostCo, NBA, Al Gore
description:
On this edition of IndeTrendence Day Jack and Miles discuss Tekashi's new music, people are boycotting CostCo for making them wear masks, Which player from the 2000s from the NBA do you wish had a longer career, and Al Gore's hot takes on the pandemic response.
